    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/453ba505f1e2e57434ff1a2972da9862.avif?t=1770969252\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>模拟历史战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《将军：古典时代》中模拟古典时代军队的大规模战争。你可以重现古代地中海地区大小国家的真实或架空战斗，让数千人同屏作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/e847127dca44c10d582f43f3888c208d.poster.avif?t=1770969252\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/e847127dca44c10d582f43f3888c208d.webm?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/e847127dca44c10d582f43f3888c208d.mp4?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管理复杂的机制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《将军：古典时代》是一款古代背景的战争游戏，这里有大规模编队移动、混乱无序的冲锋、追击、躲避、溃散、士气动摇、战争迷雾、地形效果和包抄。指挥控制模拟为即时战争游戏带来了硬核的桌游体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/ce71e2ded6d847e46c0eb54e3dc04b1d.poster.avif?t=1770969252\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/ce71e2ded6d847e46c0eb54e3dc04b1d.webm?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/ce71e2ded6d847e46c0eb54e3dc04b1d.mp4?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>指挥古典时代的军队</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《将军：古典时代》中的军队跨越了千年的古典时代，从希波战争的重装步兵和不死军到崛起的萨珊帝国对抗罗马帝国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/5e2ad46eda6b4e0fe33e904f7e6556b8.poster.avif?t=1770969252\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/5e2ad46eda6b4e0fe33e904f7e6556b8.webm?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/5e2ad46eda6b4e0fe33e904f7e6556b8.mp4?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>掌控先进的指挥和控制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >先进的指挥和控制模拟鼓励玩家思考将军的位置、作用以及何时派遣他们，在下达命令、派出信使、提供士气支持和直接战斗中进行权衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑选大量势力和单位</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含250种以上单位和约120个势力，包括不同时代的希腊化帝国、阿契美尼德波斯帝国、罗马、迦太基、高卢、日耳曼和伊比利亚部落、翁布里亚人和萨莫奈人等意大利原住民、古希腊的主要城邦、色雷斯人等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/5ae04d43b8022a846dfd3bbd87765837.poster.avif?t=1770969252\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/5ae04d43b8022a846dfd3bbd87765837.webm?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/5ae04d43b8022a846dfd3bbd87765837.mp4?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/af8402cde0cde787b9cb8d40309e5c2d.poster.avif?t=1770969252\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/af8402cde0cde787b9cb8d40309e5c2d.webm?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/af8402cde0cde787b9cb8d40309e5c2d.mp4?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义战斗选项包括：军队列表、盟友、单位、军队规模、时代、地图、部署距离、交战方、难度、电脑玩家类型/侵略性、是否使用电脑玩家（也可使用热座模式）。你可以随机化可选军队列表，也可以按时代、重要性、是否为草原军队等条件筛选随机军队。目前的历史战斗包含伊苏斯之战和拉菲亚之战，后续还会添加更多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/cf5a42d3144b0a37755df34f25ae45ce.poster.avif?t=1770969252\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/cf5a42d3144b0a37755df34f25ae45ce.webm?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064810/extras/cf5a42d3144b0a37755df34f25ae45ce.mp4?t=1770969252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>势力：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿比西尼亚/阿克苏姆</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前期（希波战争）和后期（亚历山大）阿契美尼德帝国</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >埃托利亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >安提柯</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿兰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿普利亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亚美尼亚（提格兰和非提格兰）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雅典</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿特罗帕特尼（前期/后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比提尼亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >布伦米/诺巴提亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >博斯普鲁斯</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坎帕尼亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迦太基（前期/后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >科马基尼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高加索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >达契亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伊特鲁里亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加拉太</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高卢</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >格鲁吉亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日耳曼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日耳曼（后期）步/骑部落</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希腊-巴克特里亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希腊-印度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前期希腊重装步兵（后期希腊重装步兵部队按城邦划分）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希腊化时代的希腊</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哈斯蒙尼犹太</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雅皮吉</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伊利里亚（前期/后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >印度-帕提亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >印度-斯基泰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >意大利部落</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >犹地亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡帕多西亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >贵霜（前期/后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凯里尼亚希腊（前期/后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拉丁</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利比亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利古里亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卢卡尼亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吕底亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吕基亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利西马科斯</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >马加比犹太</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >马其顿（亚历山大前期/亚历山大后期/继业者前期/继业者后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >马萨里亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >麦罗埃库施</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摩尔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纳巴泰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >努米底亚（前期/后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >培奥尼亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帕尔米拉</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帕提亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帕加马（前期/后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >福基斯</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本都（米特里达梯前期/后期和前米特里达梯）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >托勒密（前期/中前期/中后期/后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >皮洛士（前期/后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罗克索拉尼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罗马（图利乌斯/卡米卢斯/波利比乌斯/马略/帝国前期/帝国后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塞迦</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >萨莫奈</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >萨尔马提亚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >萨珊（前期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塞琉古（前期/中前期/中后期/后期）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >斯基泰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奴隶叛军</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >西班牙（伊比利亚/凯尔特伊比利亚/卢西塔尼亚/塞多留）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >斯巴达</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >斯巴达（希腊化）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >叙拉古</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塔兰托</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >底比斯</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色萨利</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色雷斯（前期/高卢/希腊化/罗马附庸）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >翁布里亚</p></li></ul>",
